  "texts": [
    "As illustrated in the accompanying figure, an analysis of the table reveals that the emotional labels of certain sentences align with the scores in the \"M\" column, derived from multimodal analysis.",
    "For instance, consider the sentence \"um yeah the special effects were ok,\" with an actual label of \"0\" indicating a neutral emotion.",
    "The \"M\" column scores it as \"1.1852,\" which is close to neutral, suggesting that the text modality's analysis in this case coincides with the actual emotion.As shown in Table 7.",
    "In other cases, such as \"because I truly love an action flick, action comedy flick even better, right,\" the actual label is \"1.6,\" denoting a positive emotion.",
    "The \"M\" column score is also positive at \"2.2367,\" indicating that the textual modality's analysis aligns with the actual emotion once again, which demonstrates the high accuracy of emotional analysis in the text modality."
  ]
}